<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cadastro de restaurantes</title>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/cadastro_rest.css">
    <script src="/js/cadastro_rest.js" defer></script>
    <script src="/js/darkmode.js" defer></script>

    

</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg  p-0">
            <a class="navbar-brand p-0" href="/restaurantes"><img id="logo-image" src="/img/logo-black.png" alt=""></a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler me-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#header-options"
                    aria-controls="header-option" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div id="header-options" class="collapse navbar-collapse ">
                    <div class="navbar-nav m-0">
                        <div class="nav-item me-auto" id="cadastro-ajuda">
                            <div id="ajuda" class="op dropdown">
                                <button id="button-ajuda" class="btn dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                                    aria-expanded="false">
                                    Ajuda
                                </button>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#"></a>Central de Ajuda</li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#"></a>Perguntas Frequentes</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="user-info-holder">
                                <button id="user_img" class="btn navbar-nav mb-2  mb-lg-0">
                                  <img class="options-nav" src="/img/user.png">
                                </button>
                                <div id="user_info" class="collapse">
                                  <div class="user-img-box">
                                    <img src="/img/user.png" alt="">
                                  </div>
                  
                                  <div id="info_section" class="d-flex flex-column gap-4">
                                    <p id="info_full_name">Full Name: </p>
                                    <p id="info_email">Email: </p>
                                    <p id="info_phone">Phone: </p>
                                  </div>
                  
                                  <button id="logout-button" class="btn btn-primary">Logout</button>
                                </div>
                                <div id="user_login_page" class="collapse">
                                  <p>Efetue o login!</p>
                                  <button class="btn btn-primary" id="button-entrar">Login</button>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                        
                </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div id="text-holder" class="d-flex flex-column">
            <h3 id="text">Sua empresa necessita de<br>uma <span id="text-colored">gestão ágil?</span></h3>
            <div id="text-2">
                <h4>Sua empresa pede</h4>
                <img id="logo-cadastro" src="/img/logo-white.png" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cadastro-holder">
            <form id="cadastroForm" class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between" action="/cadastro-restaurantes" method="post">
                <h3>Cadastre seu negócio!</h2>
                <div class="form-inputs d-flex flex-column mt-4">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column container-fluid p-0 gap-3">
                        <label for="user_name">Nome da Loja</label>
                        <input  type="text" placeholder="FoodSpace" name="rest_name" id="user_name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column container-fluid p-0 gap-3 pt-3">
                        <label for="user_name">Endereço</label>
                        <input class="" type="text" placeholder="Av. Juscelino Kubitschek de Oliveira, 11800" name="rest_adress" id="user_phone">
                    </div>
                    <p class="d-flex p-0 gap-2 pt-4">Horário de funcionamento:</p>
                    <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-between p-0 pt-1">
                        <div class="funcionamento gap-3 d-flex flex-column">
                            <label for="user_name">Abre às:</label>
                            <input class="" type="text" placeholder="12:00" name="rest_open" id="user_pw">
                        </div>
                        <div class="funcionamento gap-3 d-flex flex-column">
                            <label for="user_name">Fecha às:</label>
                            <input class="" type="text" placeholder="19:30" name="rest_close" id="user_pw">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column container-fluid p-0 gap-3 pt-3">
                        <label for="user_name">E-mail</label>
                        <input class="" type="text" placeholder="foodspace@gmail.com" name="rest_email" id="user_email">
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex pt-4">
                        <p>Esse site é protegido pelo reCAPTCHA e está sujeito à Política de Privacidade e aos Termos de Serviço do Google.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id="button-cadastro-loja" type="submit" class="mt-3">Cadastre-se</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>